{"story":{"group_1":[{"armatureList":[{"animation":["action"],"armatureId":1,"filePath":"resource/image_native/effect/story/general/3507_film_frame.ExportJson","zOrder":"messageBack"}],"autoTurnLast":0.2,"bg":"bg_adv_20142.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"pos":0,"soulGem":0},{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/scene0/mt_calender_day-xx.png","posX":-4,"posY":-50,"visible":"appear","zOrder":"messageFront"}],"turnChangeIn":"fadeIn"},{"bgm":"bgm02_anime06","chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-1"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That wasn't pleasant, was it?","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-2"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...Sorry you had to see that."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-3"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]So...@You wanted to cure your mother's illness?"},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200906,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-4"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well, I sort of already expected her@to respond that way."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-5"},{"id":200501,"motion":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]...You know, she used to be really kind."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-6"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]But ever since she saw her own death,@she's been like a different person."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"motion":100,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-7"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]To her, fortunes are always absolute..."},{"chara":[{"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-8"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So even beyond the fear of death, she@can't accept her predictions being wrong."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-9"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]That's just how she is..."},{"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":200906,"motion":200,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-10"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, it seems she doesn't need@a miracle like that."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"motion":300,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-11"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yes...I suppose not."},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-12"}],"nameAvRight":"Mami","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I wanted to fight alongside you@as a Magical Girl, but..."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-13"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Well...I'm honestly not really the type@to risk my life to do anything."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp3.json","id":200906,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-14"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]So, you might want to find@another candidate."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"textAvClear":1},{"chara":[{"id":200501,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-15"},{"id":810000,"motion":0,"pos":2,"posX":40,"posY":0}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]I guess we'll have to, Kyubey."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-16"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]That's a shame. But if it's what@Mabayu chooses, then so be it."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":100,"pos":0,"soulGem":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-17"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Sorry about dragging you out here..."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-18"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I must say, you humans truly@are interesting."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp3.json","id":200906,"motion":1,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-19"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mabayu","textAvColor":"textMabayu","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]Interesting...?"},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-20"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyubey","textAvColorRGB":"255255255","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]I thought that self-preservation was@a core instinct for living things."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-21"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyubey","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]Yet, individuals can have priorities@that override those instincts."},{"chara":[{"id":810000,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-22"}],"nameAvRight":"Kyubey","textAvRight":"[fontSize:20]To me, it seems like people would@be happier without emotions."},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_040.exp3.json","id":200501,"motion":100,"pos":0,"voiceFullAuto":"fullvoice/section_104213/vo_full_913002-002-23"}],"nameAvLeft":"Mami","textAvColor":"textMami","textAvLeft":"[fontSize:20]*Sigh*@You're saying weird things again..."},{"autoTurnLast":0.2,"item":[{"anchor":"skip","path":"resource/scenario/img/